description:
Lycanthropy affects those bitten with a transformational affliction. Werewolves succumb to a primal urge, and the ensuing frenzy is always a violent one. What they lose in sanity and control, they more than make up in sheer aggression and formidable strength&hellip;

Using an Afflicted skill line, werewolves produce a heavy damage output in multiple battle forms, but they must transform in order to do so. When they transform, they&rsquo;re unable to use other skill lines. Naturally, they will also induce lots of fatigue with such exertions.

Created by Molag Bal and in direct conflict with your mortal soul, vampirism is commonly seen as a blight, as victims struggle against an insatiable thirst for blood. But the afflicted may find that such damnation results in a surge of power well worth the cost of their soul&hellip;

Vampires, also an Afflicted skill line, do not rely as much on straightforward damage but have numerous vampiric abilities. Mist Form, Hypnosis, and other skills take advantage of playing a supporting role and establish vampires as creatures of the night!

Something reaches for you from the dark. Will you grasp it?

Each player unstacks a card in front of him with a colorful symbol and a theme. If the colored symbol is the same as the card in front of another player, the first one who finds a word that respects the theme of the card in front of his opponent wins the said card. Adding the prohibition of repeating a word already expressed around the table and a dice that sometimes invites itself into the game to create new inter-sign duels and you have there a game of speed to tie your neurons. The waterfalls of answers as the cards won are removed that rediscover the old cards creating new duels from old cards displayed in front of everyone around the table will freeze or speed up everyone&rsquo;s response times as it relaunches duels.

&bull;&bull;&bull;

Chaque joueur d&eacute;pile une carte devant lui avec un sympbole color&eacute; et un th&egrave;me. Si le symbole color&eacute; est le m&ecirc;me que la carte devant un autre joueur, le premier qui trouve un mot respectant le th&egrave;me de la carte devant son adversaire gagne la dite carte. Ajouter &agrave; cela l'interdiction de r&eacute;p&eacute;ter un mot d&eacute;j&agrave; exprim&eacute; autour de la table et un d&eacute; qui s'invite parfois dans la partie pour cr&eacute;er de nouveaux duels inter-signe et vous avez l&agrave; un jeu de rapidit&eacute; &agrave; nouer vos neurones. Les cascades de r&eacute;ponses au fil du retrait des cartes gagn&eacute;es qui red&eacute;couvrent les anciennes carte cr&eacute;ant de nouveaux duels entre les gens autour de la table vont geler ou acc&eacute;l&eacute;rer les temps de r&eacute;ponses de chacun.

This promo set adds new golden answer cards with absurd and satirical content. These include a gilded coffin with underlighting, a goldfish with post-traumatic stress disorder, Trumps and Putins secret Golden-Shower sessions, Nazi gold-tooth collections, and the gold medal in sperm-long-jump. The cards expand the variety of humorous responses players can use in the game.

&bull;&bull;&bull;

Dieses Promo-Set f&uuml;gt neue goldene Antwortkarten mit absurden und satirischen Inhalten hinzu. Diese sind ein vergoldeter Sarg mit Unterbodenbeleuchtung, ein Goldfisch mit posttraumatischer Belastungsst&ouml;rung, Trumps und Putins geheime Golden-Shower-Sessions, die Goldzahn-Sammlung der Nazis und die Goldmedaille im Sperma-Weitspritzen. Die Karten erweitern die Auswahl an humorvollen Antworten, die Spieler im Spiel verwenden k&ouml;nnen.

This promo card features a turquoise cat lounging on a chaise longue. The card grants the player the authority to make the final decision in case of rule ambiguities, with the text: "Bei Regelunklarheiten entscheide ich! Ungerecht? Egal, ich bin der Boss!" It is a display card, numbered 99, and was given for free with the purchase of "Done I Am" at the Pegasus booth during SPIEL 2025.

&bull;&bull;&bull;

Diese Promo-Karte zeigt eine t&uuml;rkise Katze, die auf einer Chaise Longue liegt. Die Karte gibt dem Spieler das Recht, bei Regelunklarheiten endg&uuml;ltig zu entscheiden. Der Text lautet: &bdquo;Bei Regelunklarheiten entscheide ich! Ungerecht? Egal, ich bin der Boss!&ldquo; Es handelt sich um eine Auslagekarte, Nummer 99, die kostenlos beim Kauf von "Fertig Ich Habe" am Pegasus-Stand auf der SPIEL 2025 vergeben wurde.

The Risky Durian promo set adds three durian tiles with values 4, -2, and -2. These tiles can be incorporated into the main game to introduce additional scoring opportunities and strategic choices. The promo was available with the purchase of the base game at SPIEL 2025.

&bull;&bull;&bull;

Das Risky Durian Promo-Set f&uuml;gt drei Durian-Pl&auml;ttchen mit den Werten 4, -2 und -2 hinzu. Diese Pl&auml;ttchen k&ouml;nnen in das Basisspiel integriert werden und bieten zus&auml;tzliche M&ouml;glichkeiten zur Punktewertung und strategische Entscheidungen. Das Promo-Set war beim Kauf des Hauptspiels auf der SPIEL 2025 erh&auml;ltlich.

The expansion contains components and rules for two new variants:
Resurrection adds a static resurrection cube which can be used to bring eliminated cubes back into play;
You Only Live Thrice adds an extra sceptre per player, and changes the goal of the game to the elimination of all opponent's sceptres.

In Чакра ("Chakra"), each player has a board that shows the seven chakras they must fill with gems that represent the energy flowing in their body. To score points, a player must harmonize each of their chakras in the best possible way.

This edition comes in a box with the Chakra: Yin Yang expansion.

&bull;&bull;&bull;
Спокойствие и расслабленность. Именно с таким настроем рекомендуется играть в настольную игру Чакра. Игрокам предстоит избавляться от негативной энергии, гармонизировать чакры с помощью разноцветных кристаллов и медитировать. Кто первым гармонизирует 5 чакр и достигнет дзена?

Чакра &mdash; очень красивая семейная игра, в которой нужно заполнить свой планшет цветными кристаллами, чтобы с помощью цепочки действий привести чакры в полную гармонию.

Игра поставляется в одной коробке с дополнением "Инь и Ян".

В дополнении появляются новые модули:
- модуль с белыми кристаллами, которые при соединении с чёрными кристаллами очищают чакру и игрок получает инь или ян;
- модуль с заданиями, выполнение которых даёт дополнительные победные очки;
- модуль с жетонами силы, позволяющими использовать бонусное действие за гармонизацию чакры;
- модуль с картами мастерства, позволяющими использовать способность после каждой медитации.

Breachers of the Bone Belfry is a merciless horror mystery adventure set in a sinister demonworld. Have you ever wished your favorite hero would get a chance at resurrection, however slim? Now you have it. But within the Belfry&rsquo;s walls lies a fate that may be much worse that death itself, for death is only the beginning&hellip;

Also featuring three new classes usable in your regular games: the paladin of death, the succubus and the necromingo.

&mdash;description from the back of the book

Das Wissensspiel Mainz is a quiz game about the German city of Mainz, the Bundesland Rheinland-Pfalz and Germany by Der St&auml;dte-Spiel-Verlag and Hugendubel.

&bull;&bull;&bull;

Das Wissensspiel mit &uuml;ber 1.000 Fragen aus deiner Stadt, der Region, dem Bundesland und Deutschland

Tidying up a magical mansion is no easy task since even the rooms here won&rsquo;t stay still! Help the little monsters straighten up the house. Work in a team to put everything back where it belongs before the clock strikes twelve!

The players take turns starting with the first player and continuing clockwise.

During your turn you are allowed two movements and however many free actions before, in-between or after your movements:

     pick up an item if you have an empty hand;
     put an item away (now it belongs to the right place);
     throw an item (to another character or to an empty slot);
     exchange items.


Whenever the turn comes back to the first player, they move the clock hand to the next hour.

Players need to put away all items before the clock srtikes 12.

-description from publisher

From the Avalanche Press webpage&hellip;

&ldquo; Several times a year, when we feel like it, the Golden Journal brings Gold Club members some fun extras for their Avalanche Press games. Our new-model Golden Journal features a &ldquo;real&rdquo; booklet, just like a small magazine, and a small set of die-cut, silky-smooth playing pieces.

On the morning of 9 April 1940, two German infantry divisions and a tank-reinforced motorized brigade surged over the border into Denmark. Airborne landings helped pave the way, and some of the troops landed on the Danish islands from German warships. The small Danish Army, with one day&rsquo;s preparation as the government hoped to avoid provoking the Germans, resisted for about four hours and could not stop the occupation. Total casualties are still unclear, but about two dozen Danes and slightly fewer Germans were killed in the sporadic fighting.

Golden Journal No. 60: 9 April 1940 is a Panzer Grenadier expansion based on this brief campaign. We cover all of the (small) battles that took place. Along with those four new Panzer Grenadier scenarios, you get 24 new die-cut and silky-smooth playing pieces. You&rsquo;ll need Road to Dunkirk to play the scenarios.

The Danes get their motorcycle-mounted 20mm anti-tank guns, which might not sound like much of a threat, but the Germans only have light tanks that can&rsquo;t stand up to these mighty Danish weapons. The Danes are at a real disadvantage in the historical scenarios, as they&rsquo;re outnumbered and unprepared, but they could easily have been ready to put up a real fight, and you can play that out, too.&rdquo;

Devious Babies is a highly strategic game, inspired by the classic tale of two-faced babies and frightened parents. Players take turns attacking each other with their babies-please use the Baby cards and not actual tiny humans-and drawing cards from the deck.

The game continues until somebody wins. How do you win? Funny you should ask&hellip; You win the game by being the first player to hold captive 4 Parent cards of the same type or by being the only player not killed by the Reaper Baby. Whatever happens first&hellip;

&mdash;description from the publisher

Snowdonia is the scenario-based, worker placement railway-building classic; this special edition boasts gorgeous all-new artwork; faster and easier set-up; and a new scenario - Stockton and Darlington, celebrating the birth of the modern railway 200 years ago.

The special edition differs from the original Snowdonia as follows:
- All new art & Graphic design;
- Upgraded components;
- Has a double-sided board for the two included scenarios (rather than previous card system); and,
- Side A of the board is the Snowdon Mountain Railway; side B is a brand new scenario for the Stockton and Darlington railway.

In The Cozy Hut, you build a secluded hut deep in the forest and spend several months there, leaving behind the troubles and burdens of modern life. Long ago, the writer and philosopher Henry David Thoreau did the same: he lived alone in the woods by a pond called Walden for two years, two months, and two days. With his own hands, he built a small hut, planted garden beds, made a stove, and sealed the cracks with moss and clay. He brought from town only nails, lamp oil, and books. The world of nature and solitude gave Thoreau many wonderful discoveries &mdash; and the manuscript of what would become his masterpiece, &ldquo;Walden, or Life in the Woods.&rdquo;

Inspired by this beautiful book, this game invites you to capture the spirit of philosophical tranquility. Following in Thoreau&rsquo;s footsteps, you will build a small forest hut in search of warmth and inner peace. Perfection and comfort are not the goal here &mdash; something will always be missing. Your aim is a cozy hut: a place with a minimum for the body and a maximum for the soul.

&mdash;description from the designer

The cult game &ldquo;Never have I ever...&rdquo; is finally available in an edition for your anniversary, or date night. Whether on a Sunday afternoon in the park, as an alternative to Netflix, for cuddling on the sofa, for game night with other couples, or simply as a fun conversation starter: with this party classic, you'll not only get to know each other better, but you'll also have lots to laugh about!
Over 60 funny and spicy &ldquo;Never have I ever...&rdquo; statements for unlimited fun. The many cheeky prompts lead to surprising revelations and bring sizzling details to light: &ldquo;Did you really...?&rdquo; &ndash; &ldquo;I don't believe it!&rdquo; &ndash; &ldquo;Why have you never told me that before?&rdquo;

&mdash;description from the publisher
